{"type": "article", "id": 33965, "title": "江南布衣上市，以及，推荐一个苹果设备外壳品牌 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-01T02:58:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34498, "name": "Apple 外壳"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}, {"id": 6869, "name": "江南布衣"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 34499, "name": "Uniqfind"}, {"id": 34500, "name": "ingenious"}, {"id": 893, "name": "隈研吾"}, {"id": 13245, "name": "水原希子"}, {"id": 22760, "name": "荒木经惟"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161101101708k3DrXZlyRj4gIn05.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/michael-kingston-alixpartners-digital-practice-10694364/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国咨询公司 AlixPartners 聘用新的数字化业务总监</b></a> |  Michael Kingston 将担任 AlixPartners 的数字化业务总监。Michael Kingston 在零售行业有超过 20 年的经验，此前他曾担任美国高档百货连锁商店 Neiman Marcus 的高级副总裁，同时担任集团的信息主管。这次任职，则是 AlixPartners 对 Michael Kingston 数字化管理成绩的肯定。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/macys-sells-five-stores-to-general-growth-properties-10694360/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅西百货向 GGP 集团出售五家店铺</b></a> | 周一，美国大型地产公司 General Growth Properties 斥资 4600 万美元，买下了梅西百货的五家店铺。GGP 成立于 1954 年，在美国拥有多家购物中心及写字楼。此次交易中的五家店铺，GGP 计划另作他用。而梅西从 GGP 租用的 Tysons Galleria 店将继续维持租约。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1477908599413.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">江南布衣集团昨日登陆港股市场，首日收涨 4.89%</a> </b>| 昨日，江南布衣有限公司在香港联交所挂牌上市，开盘价为 6.55 港元，收盘价为 6.87 港元，上涨了 4.89%，总成交额为 5858.55 万港元，该公司市值为 34.35 亿港元。截止至今年 6 月 30 日，该集团共有 1316 家门店，<a href=\"http://ch.acnnewswire.com/article.asp?art_id=33141\" rel=\"nofollow\">据招股书显示，集团在 2016 财年的收入同比上涨了 17.9%，至 19 亿人民币</a>。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/nobuyoshi-araki-x-supreme-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 2016 秋冬系列</a>推出了与日本著名摄影师荒木经惟联名的企划，该企划由水原希子出镜演绎，作品延续了荒木经惟一贯的叙述式情色摄影风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101349Q3ShOJ58w64oFNuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101358mclXTUysQxuZA3eM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101358FTScqYwLB5km0QNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101358W2HoMPeCU8uSNa59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101407l0BySp7fIOLrdHJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101407aAU6GK2lDNTofEdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611011014076WLACDSaze0ElBxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611011014085UKgaExOrC80Fnpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101415cAfLHaBCtDZ0W48J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101421esmXSIk4oiHVfGh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>新晋户外潮牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/ingenious-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> ingenious 发布 2016 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>。该系列名为 Nature，品牌以大热的大地色系为主调，搭配极具几何感的剪裁设计，整体造型还挺简约好看的。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101315eZFRGPip3D9s2Aud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101315gcEboh31fZ68w5d7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101315cFqHBmvtR49ienCy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101317zVRmSaqPMYwfiKZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101317zvP1McbQ8mZWNfXk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101319Ksz61t0PgWYunSdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611011013193OpsGZlJ6uIrCQj0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101335eSrd27vjV458pNDY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101335tBx9gruhqHNvyP1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101808nsxDCyAqolYLjhI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101814Qwe60DCBrv7puAaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>隈研吾为日本露营品牌 snow peak 设计了可以被用于野外流动生活的<a href=\"https://store.snowpeak.co.jp/sp/jyubako/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“住箱”</a>。这个移动式住箱看上去就像是一个普普通通的木盒，它有内置的 LED 灯和床架，其它的家具均可定制。现在，这款住箱已经面向企业贩售，预计明年春天完全公开贩售，具体价格 350 万日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101246CyLVDhA1euWSiM8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101254A7fCsSiFYrzeW4yM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101303IpWEPVUeu2YD8rJt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101303nwAENe2fx0rZMkTP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>推荐一个 Apple 外壳品牌。<a href=\"https://www.uniqfind.com/pages/about-us\" rel=\"nofollow\">Uniqfind </a>此前因设计“爆破 samsung”而出名。最近，它公开云石外壳新作，并带来了湖水色、桃红色等多个色调，同时设有 iPhone 7、MacBook Pro、Air 等不同尺寸。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101219RgrHnmsFZDzfwWyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101226xXj45TIRv2Lu013b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101226nGEFKtohpSiRPXUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101226JgbIQWjBiMcAKCyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101233dL2Jcs6iko8wQ10I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101238KIABM0H5oumTZ18p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/dane-dehaan-prada-2017-resort\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 的 2017 度假系列 lookbook </a>中，请来了 Dane DeHaan 出境。这也是他继 2014 春夏和 2013 春夏男装系列之后再度担任 Prada 的代言人。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611011012010Anmj79Gq5tMw4f8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101201VSdlhMt72FeKXnTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101201JW9VgurEvYC61NAU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101207YVkr2J4HCf8WLviR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161101101207IxGszayjcVAvnhem.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}